data.description: Unique corner lot residence! Whether you're enjoying your morning coffee on the second-story balcony or preparing dinner on the spacious kitchen island, this house will exude a homely vibe from the day you move in. The living room has been enhanced with luxury vinyl flooring instead of carpet, featuring a fireplace and abundant natural light streaming through the oversized windows. This 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home boasts upgraded light fixtures and ceiling fans. The master suite includes a bathroom, walk-in closet, double door entry, and a private exterior balcony. All appliances are included, and each bedroom comes with its own walk-in closet. Nestled in a charming neighborhood with a pond just across the street, this home offers a cozy and inviting atmosphere. All information obtained from seller and public records.
